{"tid":35089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"📰【恐襲20死傷】木無表情行過以為搵媽媽 尼國兩7歲女竟是人肉炸彈","createTime":"2016-12-12T00:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T00:49:08.000Z","uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64a59513d0b2745121f09fb99ce3df318fbe2e92","tid":35089,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:33:27.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞兩名年僅7歲的女童周日在東北部一個市集發動自殺式襲擊，釀成1死19傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發於杜古里市（Maiduguri）。暫未有組織承認發動襲擊，但襲擊手法似是激進伊斯蘭組織「博科聖地」（Boko Haram）所為。「博科聖地」通常利用婦孺發動自殺式襲擊，尤其在杜古里市所在的博爾諾州，而此州正是「博科聖地」的發源地。<br />\n一名民兵成員表示，見到兩名女童從她面前行過，毫無表情，向家禽檔步去，以為她們在尋找媽媽，原來是引爆炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161212/56035406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161212%2F56035406&d=KZbxA7Wxwq2HMr5tXvM3t4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=1ad3c745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161212%2F56035406&h=3917bd5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161212/56035406</a>"},{"pid":"08d43aa1ad5463f3591b468546cd21ced8cee3c0","tid":35089,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}